SIEMENS SUSTAINABILIT Y REPORT 2023 90

Actions and results We actively promote diversity, equity, and inclusion by creating

a working environment that is open and welcoming to all people.

Global LGBTQIA+- Standards and further activities Siemens supports the UN Initiative for Global LGBTQIA+-

Standards of Conduct for Companies.1

In alignment with the Diversity Charter, Siemens and its General Works Council have initiated activities like “Respect and Appreciation,” which sponsors local projects intended to bring these values to life for our people in Germany.